snippet.title: Play Ball Video Game 1975 Gremlins San Diego Lefty Casey
snippet.description: Play Ball Video Game 1975 by Gremlins in San Diego. Remote is one button.  Lefty and Casey are the players.  Has a San DIego Game of Skill Permit(no. 1495) that expired June of 1976.
